<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">which itself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 is a volcano in Ecuador, located about 55 km southwest of Quito. 
<REF ID="229.2" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="name" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="plain">Illiniza</REFEX>
